full_description:

Speaker:: Laysa Uchoa

Track: PyCon: Python Language
Python 3.10 is out and a new way of thinking about programming was brought to the Python language - Pattern Matching. We will go through how to use this feature in different scenarios and you will learn how simple, yet powerful Pattern Matching really is. 

This talk and you, it is a match!


Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2022 conference, April 11-13 2022.
https://2022.pycon.de
More details at the conference page: https://2022.pycon.de/program/PYS7G8
Twitter: https://twitter.com/pydataberlin
Twitter: https://twitter.com/pyconde
